-- Skoda Auto Investigates New Production Locations in Russia, Mfd Reports
-- Ladka Bauerova
-- 2010-06-22T05:30:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-22/skoda-auto-investigates-new-production-locations-in-russia-mfd-reports.html

          
          
             Skoda Auto, the Czech unit of
Volkswagen AG, is scouting locations in Russia for a new
production facility,  Mlada Fronta Dnes  reported, citing union
chief and a board member Jaroslav Povsik.  
 One of the locations considered by Skoda is the city of
Smolensk, the newspaper said.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Ladka Bauerova in Prague at 
 lbauerova@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        